	* grp/fgetgrent.c (buffer): Make file local variable.
	(free_mem): New function.  Call for malloc debugging.

1999-06-08  Ulrich Drepper  <drepper@cygnus.com>

	* ctype/ctype.h: Protect __tobody code by __extension__.

